(26, 1, '2019-05-13 19:10:31', '2019-05-13 19:10:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We only let the best instructors join us. Our instruction demonstrates that fear and anxiety will not prevent students from driving if they are seriously motivated. We teach innovative solutions to the complex traffic problems that confront frustrated motorists.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"row flex\">\n	<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n		<div class=\"pakageBlock\">\n			<h3>Price for teen classes</h3>\n			<ul>\n<li><strong>$239</strong> Behind the wheel for One Student<br><em><u><strong>$199</strong> If two teen sign up together</u></em></li>\n<li><strong>$280</strong> Drivers education class</li>\n<li><strong>$60</strong> 90 minute presentation</li>\n<li><strong>$150</strong> Re-exam for knowledge test</li>\n			</ul>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n		<div class=\"pakageBlock\">\n			<h3>Prices for adult classes</h3>\n			<ul>\n<li><strong>$80</strong> 2 hours</li>\n<li><strong>$70</strong> 1-1/2 hour</li>\n<li><strong>$50</strong> 1 hour</li>\n<li><strong>$350</strong> Package 10 hours</li>\n<li><strong>$140</strong> DMV road test</li>\n<li><strong>$500 ($250+$250)</strong> Adult wavier</li>\n<li><strong>$150</strong> Re exam class for knowledge test</li>\n<li><strong> $250</strong> Re exam class for road tes</li>\n			</ul>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:block {\"ref\":161} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"coursesDetails\">\n<h2>Courses Details</h2>\n<h3>Adult Courses</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><h4>Adult wavier course</h4><p>This course consist of two parts 36 hours of drivers education class each lesson is 50 minutes. Behind the wheal (BTW ) 7 hours of driving and 7 hours of observation each lesson 50 minutes .Minimum completion time for BTW is seven days In this course school will administered the road test.</p></li>\n<li><h4>Re-examination course knowledge examination</h4><p>Designated for student who have failed 3 times knowledge examination at the DMV It is an 8 hour class of 50 min period each On completion of the course school will issue a certificate of completion in order to give test fourth time in DMV.</p></li>\n<li><h4>Re-examination course</h4><p>Designated for student who have failed the DMV road test 3 times. It is 7 hour driving course in order to take road test in DMV fourth time.</p></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Teen Courses</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li><h4>Drivers education class</h4><p>This is 36 hours of class room of 50 minutes each In week days max two lesson in one day. Four lesson in weekends or holidays.</p></li>\n\n	<li><h4>90 minutes parents and teen presentation</h4><p>90 minutes parent and student driver education component in –person as required by Virginia code 22.-205</p></li>\n	<li><h4>Behind The Wheel</h4><p>This course consist of 7 hours of driving and 7 hours of observation Minimum 7 days to completion.</p></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Class room timings</h3>\n<p>5 PM Till 9 pm schedule through web site</p>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Courses', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'courses', '', '', '2019-07-03 19:13:13', '2019-07-03 19:13:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/eagle/?page_id=26', 0, 'page', '', 0),
