nto your eyes.</li><li>Text messaging or reading of text messages while driving is illegal for all drivers.</li><li>Driver under age 18 are prohibited by va law from using cell phones or any other wireless communication device while driving .</li><li>Under Virginia law, the driver and all front seat passengers must wear safety belts.</li><li>All children under age 8 must be properly secured in a child safety seat when riding in vehicle</li><li>Children should ride rear facing from birth to 2 years.</li><li>If you break certain laws or repeatedly violates the laws of Virginia , your driving privilege may be suspend or revoked by the court and or DMV.</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'DMV Laws', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '205-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-18 19:22:07', '2019-06-18 19:22:07', '', 205, 'http://localhost/eagle/205-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
